WEBVTT

01:42.480 --> 01:45.200
In eight more hours, we will witness

01:45.280 --> 01:48.080
the grand reunification ceremony
of Hong Kong and China.

01:48.160 --> 01:52.240
This is a moment we have
been waiting for 155 years.

01:52.320 --> 01:52.920
WELCOME BACK, HONG KONG

01:53.000 --> 01:58.720
The midnight of July 1st, 1997
is approaching steadily.

02:09.960 --> 02:10.800
YUANLONGLI INTERNATIONAL GARDEN

02:12.040 --> 02:15.320
What was it again? Good

02:15.400 --> 02:18.240
afternoon, Sir.

02:28.520 --> 02:31.080
YUANLONGLI INTERNATIONAL GARDEN

02:46.280 --> 02:48.640
No parking here.

02:48.720 --> 02:51.160
No parking here. Go.

02:51.800 --> 02:52.880
‎Hey!

02:52.960 --> 02:54.680
Where did she go?

03:00.680 --> 03:03.760
A relative of someone here?

03:08.360 --> 03:10.280
Look. That guy.

03:10.360 --> 03:10.960
NEW YORK BLOCK

03:11.040 --> 03:12.120
Why is he in black?

03:22.800 --> 03:24.480
They didn't even pick up the kid
after they bumped into him.

03:42.320 --> 03:43.520
Qiang.

03:43.600 --> 03:44.520
Qiang.

03:51.000 --> 03:52.320
Eighteenth floor?

03:52.400 --> 03:54.360
I thought no one lived there anymore.

04:05.040 --> 04:06.000
Qiang.

04:12.760 --> 04:13.640
Do you see what's on her back…

04:13.720 --> 04:14.960
-What are you staring at?
-Oh my!

04:15.720 --> 04:16.720
Nothing.

04:17.800 --> 04:19.240
I have a meeting at the provincial office.

04:19.320 --> 04:21.000
Keep your eyes open.
Make sure nothing happens.

04:21.079 --> 04:22.120
Okay.

04:31.040 --> 04:32.960
The janitor said she went
to the 18th floor.

04:33.040 --> 04:34.320
18th floor? It's already haunted

04:34.400 --> 04:35.600
before they raided
the prostitution rings here.

04:35.680 --> 04:37.920
Eighteenth floor?
Wasn't the underground club raided?

04:38.000 --> 04:39.200
Where did they go?

05:29.680 --> 05:31.120
It's you, Ma Qiang?

05:31.960 --> 05:34.880
Weird. Both fire exits are locked.

05:34.960 --> 05:36.800
Where could those two have gone?

05:36.880 --> 05:39.360
Don't touch anything.
Go downstairs to find them.

05:41.640 --> 05:42.880
What's the matter, Wang?

05:48.000 --> 05:50.360
Wang Wuluan. What are you doing?

06:00.400 --> 06:02.760
Why is there a pair of footprints here?

06:34.840 --> 06:36.040
There's no one in there.

06:44.720 --> 06:49.360
Call 110!

07:00.040 --> 07:03.240
Puking before you go to work.

07:03.320 --> 07:07.400
This must be your first day, rookie.

07:07.480 --> 07:09.960
I'm getting motion sickness.
You drove too fast.

07:10.040 --> 07:14.240
Liu. After you're done puking,
come here. I want to talk to you.

07:14.320 --> 07:16.880
Come here. I want to talk to you.

07:20.600 --> 07:21.760
Listen.

07:25.560 --> 07:26.440
Listen.

07:26.520 --> 07:28.960
We've been asked
to team up at the last minute.

07:29.040 --> 07:32.080
Even though it's quite ad hoc,
rules must be established.

07:32.160 --> 07:34.440
I know. Captain Feng said
you came to assist

07:34.520 --> 07:35.800
and would go back after a week.

07:35.880 --> 07:37.040
-They asked me to…
-They asked you

07:37.120 --> 07:38.600
not to give me any trouble. Right?

07:39.880 --> 07:41.920
They asked me to guide you
through our work.

07:42.960 --> 07:45.960
Who's guiding whom now? You're a rookie.

07:46.040 --> 07:47.920
Do you know how many years
I've been doing this?

07:50.280 --> 07:51.720
But you've been working
in a police station.

07:51.800 --> 07:53.480
I studied for six years to become
a criminal police officer.

07:55.000 --> 07:56.440
You only know the theories.

07:56.520 --> 07:57.960
Enough chatting.

07:58.040 --> 08:00.600
The old guide the young.
That's the rule in the squad.

08:00.680 --> 08:02.680
Captain Feng only told me
to partner up with you.

08:02.760 --> 08:05.200
Even in a partnership,
there's a pecking order.

08:05.280 --> 08:06.880
I'm the mentor. You're my apprentice.

08:06.960 --> 08:09.120
When we work, you listen to me.

08:14.400 --> 08:16.520
So, how do you want to proceed today?

08:16.600 --> 08:17.800
That's the right attitude.

08:17.880 --> 08:21.640
Listen. I was in charge of Yuanlongli
when I was working in the police station.

08:21.720 --> 08:24.040
Back then, the workers dug out a cenotaph.

08:24.120 --> 08:27.880
After that, the residents
became paranoid and superstitious.

08:27.960 --> 08:29.560
They keep calling the police for nothing.

08:30.160 --> 08:33.000
-So?
-So, we stay put.

08:33.080 --> 08:34.559
We let them cool their heads.

08:34.640 --> 08:36.000
I disagree.

08:36.080 --> 08:39.799
If paranoia isn't solved in time,
it might evolve into a collective risk.

08:39.880 --> 08:42.320
Did I just establish
the pecking order for nothing?

08:42.400 --> 08:44.480
I'm your mentor. You're my apprentice.

08:44.560 --> 08:46.320
-If I tell you to do this…
-Mr. He.

08:46.400 --> 08:48.160
Can we work now?

08:48.760 --> 08:51.760
Mr… Mr. He? You think I'm a mechanic?

08:51.840 --> 08:53.480
More like someone who fixes gas lights.

08:53.560 --> 08:54.600
What gas lights?

08:54.680 --> 08:56.440
Gaslighting. Gaslight.

08:56.520 --> 08:58.000
Did you just tell me to bugger off?

08:58.560 --> 09:00.520
So rude.

09:05.680 --> 09:08.920
Something bad happened
in Yuanlongli just now.

09:09.520 --> 09:12.440
Do you want to know?
A woman was carrying a man on her back

09:12.520 --> 09:14.560
up to the 18th floor.

09:14.640 --> 09:16.080
How creepy!

09:16.160 --> 09:17.760
A man and a woman.

09:17.840 --> 09:20.240
Both covered in black.

09:20.320 --> 09:21.160
Gone.

09:21.240 --> 09:23.200
Not even bones left.

09:23.280 --> 09:25.280
I saw with my own eyes.

09:25.360 --> 09:26.880
You saw with your own eyes.

09:28.920 --> 09:30.680
Meng. Come here.

09:34.360 --> 09:37.760
Not even bones left. I see.

09:37.840 --> 09:40.680
Officer He. That's my cloak.

09:40.760 --> 09:42.520
Didn't you say it killed two people?

09:42.600 --> 09:43.640
It's now evidence.

09:43.720 --> 09:46.320
I have to keep it to examine it.

09:46.400 --> 09:48.160
Who else witnessed it?

09:48.240 --> 09:49.880
‎YUANLONGLI INTERNATIONAL GARDEN

09:53.000 --> 09:55.280
‎POLICE

09:56.360 --> 09:58.320
Calling the police
for the slightest inconvenience.

09:58.400 --> 09:59.600
How many times has it been?

09:59.680 --> 10:01.200
You two.

10:01.280 --> 10:02.800
One is from the residents committee.
One is from the security team.

10:02.880 --> 10:05.880
Instead of dispelling
the superstition, you fanned it.

10:05.960 --> 10:08.160
Making a fake police call is a crime.
Do you understand?

10:08.240 --> 10:09.640
Yes.

10:09.720 --> 10:11.840
There's no victim and no culprit.

10:11.920 --> 10:13.360
Their relatives
also didn't call the police.

10:13.440 --> 10:15.120
There's nothing to file a case here.

10:15.200 --> 10:17.000
Besides, the police already came here.

10:17.080 --> 10:19.360
Come. Sign it.

10:20.920 --> 10:23.840
One more week,
and I'll go back to my previous post.

10:23.920 --> 10:26.200
Do you get what I mean?

10:26.280 --> 10:27.920
It's the last sprint.

10:28.000 --> 10:30.680
Don't go to the criminal department
and bother me for something trivial.

10:30.760 --> 10:31.920
If I get a case,
I won't be able to go back.

10:32.840 --> 10:34.600
-Just sign it.
-I… Where do I sign it?

10:36.920 --> 10:38.200
This young man is…

10:39.040 --> 10:41.280
Oh, he's Liu. My apprentice.

10:41.360 --> 10:42.920
He just graduated.
It's his first day at work.

10:43.000 --> 10:45.200
He's new here.
Do look after him, will you?

10:46.560 --> 10:48.920
Hello. I'm Ran. R-A-N.

10:49.880 --> 10:51.040
Also, I'm not his…

10:57.800 --> 10:59.560
WITNESS' STATEMENT

11:03.480 --> 11:05.200
Hi. Are you Li Tieling?

11:05.800 --> 11:08.200
So the woman and the old man
disappeared when you turned around.

11:08.840 --> 11:11.640
Yes. The woman was wearing a white dress
and blue leather heels.

11:11.720 --> 11:13.320
She vanished just like that.

11:13.400 --> 11:15.680
-Do you want to know how they vanished?
-Yes.

11:15.760 --> 11:18.000
Re-enact what you did
when you chased the rickshaws away.

11:18.080 --> 11:19.040
Then turn around and look at me.

11:19.120 --> 11:23.280
Okay. No parking here. Go. Go.

11:23.360 --> 11:24.200
Are you insane?

11:25.240 --> 11:26.120
Then I…

11:28.400 --> 11:30.560
He's gone. He's gone.

11:30.640 --> 11:31.960
I'm here.

11:34.280 --> 11:35.680
You assumed they would cross
the main road to enter the gate.

11:35.760 --> 11:37.000
But they stuck to the wall,

11:37.720 --> 11:38.760
just outside your line of vision.

11:40.160 --> 11:41.560
This is called a psychological blind spot.

11:41.640 --> 11:43.080
Watch me do it again.

11:43.160 --> 11:45.520
You explained the trick.

11:45.600 --> 11:47.520
Why bother doing it again?

11:50.080 --> 11:51.480
It's called re-enactment.

11:51.560 --> 11:53.000
According to the Western
investigation procedures,

11:53.080 --> 11:56.120
you must imagine that you're the culprit
and re-enact what they did.

11:56.200 --> 11:57.440
Enact what?

11:57.520 --> 11:58.800
Re… enact?

12:01.520 --> 12:04.200
From this place to that block,
taking the main road is the shorter route.

12:05.160 --> 12:06.920
Why did they take a detour then?

12:08.160 --> 12:09.240
Come with me.

12:12.520 --> 12:13.880
Where are we going?

12:14.840 --> 12:16.280
Case closed.

12:16.360 --> 12:17.920
They didn't ask for criminal police.

12:18.000 --> 12:20.520
Captain Feng got a call and asked us
to assess the situation personally.

12:20.600 --> 12:22.480
We didn't even enter the premises.
Isn't that too irresponsible?

12:22.560 --> 12:24.240
Irresponsible?

12:24.320 --> 12:26.240
Making a fake police call
is irresponsible.

12:26.320 --> 12:27.640
It's a waste of police resources too.

12:28.640 --> 12:32.480
Sir, we over-reacted here. Please go back.

12:32.560 --> 12:33.800
I'll just talk to Officer Qu.

12:33.880 --> 12:35.680
Wait. Officer Qu?

12:35.760 --> 12:37.560
Which one? Qu Dahai?

12:37.640 --> 12:41.960
Yes. I called 110, and Officer Qu came.

12:42.040 --> 12:42.880
He's inside the building?

12:44.560 --> 12:45.560
I'll go and take a look.

12:52.600 --> 12:55.320
YUANLONGLI INTERNATIONAL GARDEN

12:57.640 --> 12:59.800
That woman carried the old man

12:59.880 --> 13:02.600
and stood still here.
She even took off her heels.

13:03.240 --> 13:04.240
What else did she do?

13:08.840 --> 13:09.760
She did this.

13:14.000 --> 13:15.040
I can fix it.

13:22.080 --> 13:22.960
I'll pick it up.

13:32.560 --> 13:35.000
So clumsy. Hurry up.

13:40.440 --> 13:42.880
Officer Qu. Careful. The footprints.

13:50.320 --> 13:51.360
What are you doing?

13:51.960 --> 13:53.120
PATTIA CLUB

13:53.200 --> 13:56.080
He Yuanhang. What brings you here?

13:56.960 --> 13:59.080
Han. Shouhu.

13:59.160 --> 14:01.560
What are you doing here? Go back.

14:01.640 --> 14:02.520
Did I say you could go back?

14:02.600 --> 14:03.560
Continue.

14:03.640 --> 14:05.400
Your footsteps are making a mess.

14:05.480 --> 14:08.640
Are you examining
or contaminating the crime scene?

14:08.720 --> 14:10.120
Who says I'm examining the scene?

14:10.200 --> 14:12.320
I'm looking for the culprit. Continue!

14:13.680 --> 14:15.040
Touch anything if you dare.

14:15.120 --> 14:17.520
Excuse me. You're blocking the evidence.

14:20.080 --> 14:22.360
See? The criminal police are working.

14:22.440 --> 14:23.640
Now work!

14:24.560 --> 14:25.760
You little…

14:38.160 --> 14:40.840
I like him. What's his name?

14:43.800 --> 14:45.600
Ran Fangxu. My apprentice.

14:45.680 --> 14:47.200
Top scorer from People's Public Security
University of China, PPSUC.

14:47.280 --> 14:48.400
PPSUC?

14:49.600 --> 14:51.000
Your apprentice?

14:51.080 --> 14:52.960
Why would I have
brought him here with me, otherwise?

14:54.000 --> 14:54.840
Jealous?

14:55.600 --> 14:57.680
Want to join the criminal department?

14:57.760 --> 14:59.400
I can talk to Captain Feng for you.

15:00.160 --> 15:02.400
You can have him.

15:03.040 --> 15:04.200
Sounds good?

15:14.400 --> 15:16.440
This wooden plank is so annoying.

15:17.200 --> 15:18.680
Well, it's all thanks to your mentor.

15:18.760 --> 15:20.560
He did this when he raided
the prostitution ring.

15:20.640 --> 15:21.840
That's right.

15:26.080 --> 15:26.920
Let me borrow this.

15:29.400 --> 15:30.640
He is not my mentor.

15:34.360 --> 15:36.120
You liar.

15:38.520 --> 15:39.680
-Ma Qiang.
-Yes.

15:39.760 --> 15:41.600
-Open the door.
-Okay.

15:48.960 --> 15:50.600
Forgive me. I conducted an experiment.

15:50.680 --> 15:51.680
What are you doing?

15:52.640 --> 15:55.200
Seriously? It's called enaction. Right?

15:57.600 --> 15:59.560
Re-enactment.

16:01.640 --> 16:03.240
There's a nail on the door frame.

16:03.320 --> 16:04.920
The dust by the door frame is gone.

16:05.000 --> 16:08.040
I suppose someone
hung the black cloak here.

16:10.760 --> 16:12.880
The height of it is enough
to cover an adult

16:12.960 --> 16:14.640
when someone opens the door.

16:15.680 --> 16:16.800
A prank then?

16:17.520 --> 16:18.640
But there's one unanswered question.

16:18.720 --> 16:20.400
The footprints disappear here.

16:20.480 --> 16:22.280
They didn't go back the way they came.

16:22.920 --> 16:25.120
Qu Dahai and his men stepped
all over the place.

16:25.200 --> 16:26.320
How can we trace footprints now?

16:26.400 --> 16:27.600
Dust can be thick.

16:27.680 --> 16:30.000
New and old footprints have gaps.

16:30.080 --> 16:31.920
You're so thorough, Fangxu.

16:32.000 --> 16:33.040
You left no stone unturned.

16:33.120 --> 16:36.200
Unlike someone I know
who has peanuts for a brain.

16:36.280 --> 16:37.360
All empty inside.

16:37.440 --> 16:39.320
You have peanuts for a brain.

16:39.400 --> 16:40.240
Move.

16:41.440 --> 16:43.680
How can you be a criminal police
with such a bad core strength?

16:46.320 --> 16:48.160
Size 37 feet.

16:48.840 --> 16:51.920
Carrying an old man
all the way from outside.

16:53.120 --> 16:55.080
She must be a strong woman.

16:57.400 --> 17:00.240
These must be the basics
you learned in PPSUC.

17:00.320 --> 17:01.760
They don't teach you common sense.

17:04.880 --> 17:05.920
You little…

17:15.800 --> 17:16.880
What did you see?

17:22.200 --> 17:23.520
Four cigarette butts.

17:23.599 --> 17:25.240
Judging from their looks,

17:25.319 --> 17:27.359
they were used less than two hours ago.

17:27.880 --> 17:31.560
Judging from the charred ends,
the smoker was anxious.

17:31.640 --> 17:33.600
Some of them were thrown away
after a few puffs were taken.

17:35.360 --> 17:36.920
Do you recognize the brand?

17:37.000 --> 17:38.280
How much does it cost?

17:41.720 --> 17:43.520
A packet of Yuxi cigarettes.

17:43.600 --> 17:46.200
Mainly for bosses.
Twenty yuan for one packet.

17:53.880 --> 17:57.280
Are you sure there were
no footprints in the room?

17:57.360 --> 17:58.840
I guess so.

18:01.240 --> 18:02.600
We came looking for the culprit.

18:02.680 --> 18:04.240
Of course, we walked around.

18:05.240 --> 18:09.760
Then don't walk that much.

18:18.960 --> 18:22.440
‎BEIJING TRAVEL

18:27.680 --> 18:28.520
Officer He. Officer Qu.

18:28.600 --> 18:30.400
Calm down. Tell me clearly.

18:30.480 --> 18:34.520
Okay. I checked all the rooms.
There's no one.

18:34.600 --> 18:37.320
I also checked the security cameras.
No one took the elevator.

18:37.400 --> 18:41.520
Two adults couldn't possibly
vanish just like that.

18:41.600 --> 18:42.960
They must be somewhere.

18:43.040 --> 18:44.880
Both sides of the staircase
are locked from the outside too.

18:44.960 --> 18:45.800
Where else could they go?

18:46.600 --> 18:48.880
It looks like a locked room.

18:49.640 --> 18:51.400
Three paths.

18:52.400 --> 18:53.640
The staircase is locked.

18:53.720 --> 18:55.920
The elevator has security cameras.

18:56.000 --> 19:00.000
Exactly. It's weird.
That's why I called Captain Feng.

19:00.720 --> 19:04.720
I think you should file a case.

19:05.840 --> 19:07.800
File what case? What case?

19:07.880 --> 19:09.640
Let me explain everything to you.

19:10.240 --> 19:13.080
The door is locked from the outside.
You can't open it.

19:25.760 --> 19:29.120
See? They left like this.

19:29.200 --> 19:30.760
This door isn't locked.

19:30.840 --> 19:32.400
File a case?

19:32.480 --> 19:34.360
This is just a prank. Okay?

19:34.440 --> 19:36.440
Officer He. This isn't right.

19:36.520 --> 19:38.320
The staircase. The window.

19:38.400 --> 19:40.440
And the padlock. The padlock!

19:41.200 --> 19:42.400
What? Isn't it…

19:45.520 --> 19:47.400
-Surround them from both sides!
-On it!

19:59.440 --> 20:00.840
Stay right there!

20:03.760 --> 20:04.840
Wait for me.

20:04.920 --> 20:07.360
Sorry, I'm in a hurry.
Take the next one. Sorry.

20:07.440 --> 20:08.760
Stealing a lock before the police.

20:08.840 --> 20:10.280
How dare you!

20:10.360 --> 20:11.480
Stop right there.

20:12.200 --> 20:14.400
Stop right there. Stop right there.

20:15.160 --> 20:16.160
What are you doing?

20:44.920 --> 20:45.840
He Yuanhang!

20:45.920 --> 20:48.120
I caught him. He Yuanhang! Help me!

20:48.200 --> 20:49.360
Why are you yelling?

20:50.160 --> 20:51.000
Stop yelling.

20:51.080 --> 20:52.400
You took the elevator,
but you're still slow!

20:52.480 --> 20:53.680
He has already run away!

21:00.760 --> 21:02.040
Be careful.

21:02.120 --> 21:03.040
NEW YORK BLOCK

21:03.120 --> 21:04.680
Officer He!

21:06.920 --> 21:08.880
Officer He. Officer He.

21:08.960 --> 21:10.560
There are bad guys in the block.

21:10.640 --> 21:12.240
They scared my son.

21:13.800 --> 21:15.960
Were you running around
the staircase just now?

21:17.760 --> 21:19.640
Why did you go to the 18th floor?

21:19.720 --> 21:21.480
He saw everything.

21:21.560 --> 21:23.640
He even bumped into them.

21:23.720 --> 21:24.800
Tell me.

21:24.880 --> 21:27.600
Why did you lock us in the staircase?

21:27.680 --> 21:29.800
I was scared you'd come after me.

21:32.840 --> 21:34.640
Hey there. It's okay.

21:34.720 --> 21:37.000
You saw the two missing persons, right?

21:37.880 --> 21:40.000
I saw their hands.

21:40.520 --> 21:43.040
It's not human hands. They have claws.

21:52.880 --> 21:53.800
Claws?

21:53.880 --> 21:56.120
Is that coming from your exaggeration?

22:02.040 --> 22:04.360
See? I told you so.

22:04.440 --> 22:06.440
They bumped into him,

22:06.520 --> 22:08.000
and they didn't even pick him up.

22:08.080 --> 22:10.400
They bumped into him how many times?

22:10.480 --> 22:11.320
Just once.

22:11.400 --> 22:13.000
And he got bruises everywhere?

22:13.080 --> 22:14.800
It's as if he has been run over.

22:14.880 --> 22:18.080
-Little one, your bruises are…
-I fell when he chased after me.

22:26.720 --> 22:28.920
Officer He. Listen.

22:29.000 --> 22:30.920
We put the padlock
when we were checking the place.

22:31.000 --> 22:33.840
I don't care who put it there.
I just want to know if it was locked.

22:33.920 --> 22:35.040
No, it wasn't.

22:36.080 --> 22:36.960
It wasn't locked?

22:37.040 --> 22:39.520
That means those two people
could leave through that door.

22:40.280 --> 22:41.400
I guess so.

22:47.520 --> 22:48.520
You examined the place for hours,

22:48.600 --> 22:51.200
and you couldn't figure out
one simple staircase.

22:51.280 --> 22:53.520
Qu. Given your lack of competence,

22:53.600 --> 22:55.320
how am I supposed
to put in a few good words for you?

22:56.120 --> 22:57.080
Say no more.

22:59.120 --> 23:02.440
Don't just stand there.
This is just a prank.

23:02.520 --> 23:03.880
Go back and pack up. Case closed!

23:05.240 --> 23:07.120
I already told you so.

23:07.200 --> 23:09.160
The reunification of Hong Kong
is more interesting.

23:13.360 --> 23:15.520
Officer He. We need to file a case.

23:25.520 --> 23:27.560
Then explain. Why?

23:27.640 --> 23:30.320
Ma Qiang said there were
no footprints in the western corridor.

23:30.400 --> 23:32.760
They also said the cloak
took two people away.

23:32.840 --> 23:34.320
They make things up all the time.

23:34.400 --> 23:35.480
How can I believe them?

23:35.560 --> 23:37.280
Be patient. Let me finish.

23:37.360 --> 23:39.600
Just tell me what you want to do.

23:40.400 --> 23:42.360
I just want to get to the bottom
of this case.

23:42.440 --> 23:44.840
Listen carefully.
One, this isn't even a case.

23:44.920 --> 23:48.560
Two, if you want to investigate,
find another partner. Don't…

23:48.640 --> 23:50.320
Don't bother you as you're about
to go back to being the deputy director.

23:50.400 --> 23:51.720
I get it.

23:51.800 --> 23:53.520
I knew you were that kind of person
from the start.

23:53.600 --> 23:55.080
Just gaslighting people.

24:01.440 --> 24:04.200
Did you scold me just now?

24:14.520 --> 24:17.320
YUANLONGLI INTERNATIONAL GARDEN

24:24.400 --> 24:29.240
WEIYANG PUBLIC SECURITY BUREAU
NANSHAN BRANCH

24:36.720 --> 24:37.880
‎This one is…

24:44.400 --> 24:46.120
Kid.

24:46.200 --> 24:48.120
Did you see Ran?

24:48.200 --> 24:50.480
Lan? Who?

24:50.560 --> 24:52.920
R-A-N.

24:53.000 --> 24:53.960
You must be new here.

24:54.040 --> 24:56.120
-I…
-He Yuanhang. Stop yelling.

24:56.200 --> 24:57.440
Can't you see we're working here?

24:57.520 --> 24:59.280
I'm looking for Ran.

25:00.640 --> 25:02.320
Something happened in Yuanlongli again?

25:02.400 --> 25:03.960
Go back to your work.

25:04.040 --> 25:06.200
Don't pester me.

25:08.360 --> 25:11.280
Ran Fangxu is slacking
in the archive room.

25:11.880 --> 25:13.360
Do talk to him.

25:15.160 --> 25:16.560
He could've answered my call.

25:16.640 --> 25:17.920
I called him for five minutes.

25:18.000 --> 25:19.640
All of them are so lazy.

25:20.920 --> 25:22.280
He is Mr. He.

25:28.360 --> 25:31.360
Old Geezer. Why are you here again?

25:31.440 --> 25:33.800
Don't call me old geezer.

25:33.880 --> 25:34.920
Where is Ran?

25:36.920 --> 25:37.840
Why do you need him?

25:39.360 --> 25:41.160
It's none of your business. Where is he?

25:47.440 --> 25:49.200
You eat to sleep, sleep to eat.

25:49.280 --> 25:51.040
Where's your spirit?

25:51.120 --> 25:53.400
Everyone gets bored
when they work here every day.

25:54.640 --> 25:56.000
Why don't you ask them
to put me on patrol duty?

25:56.080 --> 25:57.440
Ran Fangxu!

25:58.000 --> 25:59.480
MEN'S TOILETS

26:19.480 --> 26:21.560
UNDER MAINTENANCE

26:21.640 --> 26:22.880
Ran Fangxu!

26:28.640 --> 26:29.640
Ran Fangxu!

26:29.720 --> 26:30.960
Just because you're standing
on the toilet bowl

26:31.040 --> 26:32.600
doesn't mean I won't know you're here.

26:32.680 --> 26:34.400
Come out. Open the door.

26:34.480 --> 26:36.640
Sir. I have diarrhea.

26:36.720 --> 26:37.920
I'm vomiting and pooping.

26:38.000 --> 26:39.480
I can't go anywhere.

26:39.560 --> 26:41.640
Are you an ostrich
that poops while standing?

26:41.720 --> 26:43.200
Come out now.

26:43.280 --> 26:44.520
I'll count to three.

26:44.600 --> 26:46.960
Count to 300, and I still won't come out.

26:47.040 --> 26:48.160
Just you wait.

26:49.040 --> 26:50.320
-One.
-Sir.

26:50.840 --> 26:51.800
-Two.
-What are you doing?

26:51.880 --> 26:52.800
-Sir?
-Three!

27:00.080 --> 27:01.320
Hey!

27:04.120 --> 27:05.720
Sir,

27:05.800 --> 27:07.720
I just finished this lesson plan.

27:08.840 --> 27:13.080
Oh, you and your useless theories again.

27:13.680 --> 27:16.520
I have a case that concerns my reputation.

27:17.200 --> 27:18.160
You have a reputation?

27:18.240 --> 27:19.640
I'll tell you on the way.

27:21.080 --> 27:22.840
Sir, I have work to do.

27:22.920 --> 27:24.640
Bah! This is what you call work?

27:24.720 --> 27:27.320
Some people love to be on patrol duty.

27:27.400 --> 27:29.840
Some people just want to stay
in the archive room.

27:30.440 --> 27:32.280
I can't catch a break at all.

27:33.320 --> 27:34.600
What are you implying?

27:41.040 --> 27:41.960
Mister,

27:42.480 --> 27:43.840
can you drive slower?

27:45.200 --> 27:46.280
Slower?

27:46.840 --> 27:49.400
Back then, on our first gig together,

27:50.200 --> 27:53.560
I drove slightly faster
and you got your panties in a twist.

27:55.160 --> 27:57.720
I… I have motion sickness.

27:58.440 --> 28:02.080
Besides, it wasn't like you drove fast
to investigate the case.

28:02.960 --> 28:04.360
Nonsense!

28:04.440 --> 28:06.960
Don't make it sound
like I'm irresponsible.

28:08.760 --> 28:11.120
When we first worked together,

28:11.200 --> 28:13.160
you didn't even bother memorizing
my surname.

28:13.960 --> 28:15.040
I…

28:26.720 --> 28:28.760
All right. This is it.

28:29.360 --> 28:30.560
I'm not driving over there.

28:30.640 --> 28:32.320
That place brings bad luck.

28:33.880 --> 28:34.840
Pay up.

28:34.920 --> 28:36.000
Okay.

28:36.080 --> 28:37.120
Let's go.

28:39.120 --> 28:41.040
You didn't tell me
we'd come to Yuanlongli.

28:41.640 --> 28:44.000
Come on. If I told you,
you wouldn't want to come with me.

28:44.080 --> 28:45.360
Come down now.

28:45.440 --> 28:47.120
I'm just here on a business trip.

28:47.200 --> 28:48.880
I'll be back after a week.

28:49.480 --> 28:51.280
You're going back to Beijing after a week?

28:52.400 --> 28:54.520
Did you bring me with you
for another case?

29:03.840 --> 29:05.520
His name is Han Zi'ang.

29:05.600 --> 29:07.480
He went missing less than 48 hours ago.

29:07.560 --> 29:08.600
They haven't filed the case yet.

29:08.680 --> 29:10.880
I've talked to the parents,

29:10.960 --> 29:13.360
and I think there's more
than meets the eye.

29:13.440 --> 29:15.440
I agreed to help them.

29:16.000 --> 29:19.280
After all these years, I've become
quite good at finding missing persons.

29:19.360 --> 29:21.880
They call me human radar.

29:22.600 --> 29:24.680
If there's more to the case
than meets the eye,

29:24.760 --> 29:26.120
then hand the case over to the police.

29:26.200 --> 29:28.240
As I said, they haven't
filed the case yet.

29:28.320 --> 29:31.520
I'm just a kind citizen who wants
to locate the missing child.

29:31.600 --> 29:33.760
Since we're here already,
just help me out.

29:33.840 --> 29:38.760
-My reputation is at stake here.
-Sir, I'm a teacher now.

29:38.840 --> 29:40.920
And you're retired.
We can't investigate cases anymore.

29:41.000 --> 29:42.400
Let's just leave.

29:42.480 --> 29:43.680
Don't give me excuses.

29:43.760 --> 29:45.040
Eighteen years ago,

29:45.120 --> 29:46.960
I too was eager to leave after a week.

29:47.040 --> 29:50.000
But a jerk came to me
and said I was irresponsible.

29:56.320 --> 29:57.760
Sorry, sir.

29:58.560 --> 29:59.760
Back then, it was my fault.

30:02.400 --> 30:05.360
It's not your fault.
It's not anyone's fault.

30:05.440 --> 30:07.080
If I must put the blame on something,

30:07.160 --> 30:09.600
it's on the fact that you didn't build
a good relationship with me.

30:11.680 --> 30:13.760
I didn't build
a good relationship with you?

30:13.840 --> 30:15.840
-I kept addressing you as my mentor then.
-Nonsense!

30:15.920 --> 30:17.760
Stop wasting my time. Get out of the car.

30:21.120 --> 30:23.480
Slow down. Slow down.

30:27.200 --> 30:30.040
You keep saying that you don't
want to come to Yuanlongli.

30:30.120 --> 30:32.920
But once you're in here,
you walk briskly like an eager visitor.

30:34.720 --> 30:36.280
That's because
you were gaslighting me again.

30:37.240 --> 30:40.520
I see you're not on social media.
It's not called gaslighting anymore.

30:40.600 --> 30:42.600
It's called brainwashing. Come.

30:46.040 --> 30:47.800
Let's take a break.

30:47.880 --> 30:50.360
Don't. We can't stay here for long.

30:50.440 --> 30:54.520
This building is haunted.
Once in a while, it'll kill someone.

30:54.600 --> 30:55.920
Two policemen died here.

30:56.000 --> 30:56.840
Died here?

30:56.920 --> 30:58.720
One of them was in charge of this place.

30:58.800 --> 31:01.200
-What's his name again?
-He something.

31:01.280 --> 31:03.280
When they found him, his body was impaled

31:03.360 --> 31:06.160
by a spear on this wall.

31:06.240 --> 31:07.400
It was horrifying.

31:08.440 --> 31:09.960
Quickly now.

31:10.040 --> 31:12.320
You two look horrifying.

31:12.400 --> 31:15.400
Mister. We weren't even talking about you.
Why are you yelling at me?

31:16.200 --> 31:18.080
-Sir.
-Don't hold me back.

31:18.160 --> 31:21.680
Tell me. How was I impaled on this wall?

31:28.400 --> 31:30.120
Oh my…

31:38.720 --> 31:42.800
Sir, Yuanlongli houses
a superstitious community.

31:42.880 --> 31:44.200
You know that already.

31:44.280 --> 31:45.680
Why pick a bone with them?

31:45.760 --> 31:49.000
If I don't scold them now,
the next one they curse will be you.

31:57.680 --> 31:59.320
You're dead.

31:59.400 --> 32:01.680
You can't step on the 18th floor.

32:01.760 --> 32:03.440
Yuanlongli

32:03.520 --> 32:08.960
-Eighteenth floor, 18 pillars
-Eighteenth floor…

32:09.040 --> 32:14.480
Eighteenth floor with 18 pillars

32:14.560 --> 32:19.600
Eighteen pillars
With 18 men to carry them…

32:21.000 --> 32:22.720
They are still singing the nursery rhyme?

32:22.800 --> 32:26.440
If you hadn't insisted
on investigating the truth,

32:26.520 --> 32:30.040
this so-called haunted building
would've taken more lives.

32:31.040 --> 32:36.240
Eighteenth floor with 18 pillars

32:36.320 --> 32:41.360
Eighteen bodies, 18 heads

32:52.720 --> 32:53.760
He Yuanhang.

32:54.560 --> 32:55.560
You owe me a meal.

32:55.640 --> 32:56.720
For what?

32:56.800 --> 32:59.800
WEIYANG CULTURAL CENTER

32:59.880 --> 33:01.120
Aren't you investigating a case?

33:01.200 --> 33:03.720
I jumped the queue for you
and got the report ready.

33:05.560 --> 33:08.160
Six more days till I return
to the police station.

33:08.240 --> 33:09.240
What case is this?

33:10.040 --> 33:11.680
Come on. They sent
the evidence for analysis.

33:12.280 --> 33:13.480
Two sets of fingerprints.

33:13.560 --> 33:14.480
Four cigarette butts.

33:14.560 --> 33:17.360
One cloak. And one security footage.

33:17.440 --> 33:19.000
It's all under your name.

33:22.120 --> 33:22.960
I…

33:24.000 --> 33:25.040
It was all good.

33:26.400 --> 33:29.960
Except Mr. He Yuanhang
and I don't get along well.

33:30.040 --> 33:32.040
Can you get me another partner?

33:32.120 --> 33:33.840
Changing your partner on your first day?

33:33.920 --> 33:35.080
What did He Yuanhang do?

33:35.160 --> 33:36.800
I don't think he has…

33:37.960 --> 33:40.520
Captain Feng. I'm here
to find my apprentice.

33:41.160 --> 33:42.360
Let me reiterate.

33:42.440 --> 33:43.640
I am not your apprentice.

33:43.720 --> 33:47.680
Young and petty.
It's just a term. No need to overreact.

33:47.760 --> 33:50.160
I'm not being petty.
I'm being responsible here.

33:51.080 --> 33:52.840
Captain Feng. See this?

33:52.920 --> 33:55.080
Our temperaments don't match.
Our personalities are different.

33:55.160 --> 33:57.360
We argue often,
and that'll affect our work efficiency.

33:57.440 --> 33:59.360
Since I'm going back
to the police station,

33:59.440 --> 34:01.600
why don't you give him another partner?

34:01.680 --> 34:03.760
I'll hand over whatever I'm doing to him.

34:08.199 --> 34:10.920
I see you two are putting
on an act in front of me.

34:12.159 --> 34:15.719
Just be frank. What help
do you need from me?

34:15.800 --> 34:17.239
Captain Feng.

34:17.320 --> 34:19.400
This is not an act.

34:19.480 --> 34:22.840
-I mean it. I want to break…
-Break up!

34:26.840 --> 34:28.320
-Captain Feng.
-I am.

34:34.520 --> 34:37.880
Captain Feng. The embarrassing case
from Yuanlongli.

34:37.960 --> 34:39.719
The residents have come forward.

34:39.800 --> 34:40.679
What now?

34:40.760 --> 34:43.159
He Yuanhang. Mind your words.

34:45.159 --> 34:48.920
Maybe officers like you
think it's nothing.

34:49.000 --> 34:51.679
But the residents are getting manic.

34:51.760 --> 34:55.239
They are saying the two missing persons
are the Black and White Guards.

34:55.320 --> 34:56.719
And the building is their hunting ground.

34:57.800 --> 34:59.720
And they are singing this.

34:59.800 --> 35:01.120
Yuanlongli

35:01.200 --> 35:02.680
Eighteenth floor

35:02.760 --> 35:04.320
Eighteen bodies, 18 heads

35:04.400 --> 35:05.320
Nonsense.

35:05.400 --> 35:07.640
Someone among them
is trying to spread a rumor.

35:10.240 --> 35:11.560
Captain Feng.

35:11.640 --> 35:15.560
When they were building Yuanlongli,
they found a tomb.

35:15.640 --> 35:17.120
It was a cenotaph
from the Three Kingdoms period.

35:17.200 --> 35:18.400
There were no human remains inside.

35:18.480 --> 35:21.320
The Residents Committee
just has to clarify the rumors.

35:21.400 --> 35:23.920
Why mobilize the criminal police?

35:24.000 --> 35:28.480
The problem is that Yuanlongli
is a complex neighborhood.

35:29.040 --> 35:30.920
You see all sorts of people there.

35:31.760 --> 35:33.240
Someone went missing yesterday.

35:33.320 --> 35:34.440
Then today, a nursery song
like that appeared.

35:34.520 --> 35:36.280
Everyone is scared.

35:36.360 --> 35:39.080
-Please help us find the truth.
-He Yuanhang.

35:40.840 --> 35:44.160
What was yesterday's case about?

35:44.240 --> 35:47.000
Qu Dahai had already determined
that it was just a prank.

35:47.080 --> 35:49.240
-But I…
-It wasn't a prank at all.

35:50.440 --> 35:51.360
Captain Feng.

35:52.560 --> 35:54.160
I interviewed the witnesses last night.

35:54.240 --> 35:55.360
I can confirm three things.

35:55.440 --> 35:58.480
One. There are no footprints
deeper into the corridor.

35:58.560 --> 36:00.480
Two. The security guards
put the padlock there.

36:00.560 --> 36:03.800
Three. Mr. Liang broke the glass
of the door leading to the staircase.

36:03.880 --> 36:06.840
Therefore, the exit path
Officer He described yesterday

36:06.920 --> 36:08.440
could never have existed.

36:08.520 --> 36:11.000
The disappearance of those two persons
is still an enigma.

36:15.280 --> 36:17.560
Well said! I agree with Fangxu.

36:17.640 --> 36:18.720
I also agree with him.

36:18.800 --> 36:21.800
Trivial problems, when neglected,
will fester into major problems.

36:23.280 --> 36:24.840
Rumors can be destructive.

36:38.880 --> 36:41.880
Some say that He Yuanhang
only got into the criminal department

36:41.960 --> 36:43.240
because of his connections.

36:43.320 --> 36:44.520
Take a seat.

36:46.560 --> 36:51.160
But in fact, I chose him
from among many candidates.

36:51.240 --> 36:52.520
Captain Feng.

36:52.600 --> 36:55.280
Even though he never receives
proper training,

36:55.360 --> 36:59.080
the place he's in charge of consistently

36:59.160 --> 37:00.880
has the highest clearance rate.

37:00.960 --> 37:02.600
What does this mean?

37:02.680 --> 37:07.000
It means he has something
neither of us has.

37:08.560 --> 37:10.960
In certain areas,
he will be quite helpful.

37:11.560 --> 37:16.760
But of course, you can also
help him with your expertise.

37:16.840 --> 37:18.200
Do you get what I mean now?

37:19.760 --> 37:22.280
Captain Feng,
about the case in Yuanlongli…

37:22.360 --> 37:25.360
Both of you will follow up with the case.

37:27.680 --> 37:29.880
Officer He. Don't let me keep you.
I have to go now.

37:30.800 --> 37:34.920
‎POLICE BY THE PEOPLE
‎FOR THE PEOPLE

37:44.640 --> 37:48.640
MISSING DOG

38:08.800 --> 38:09.840
Stop.

38:11.000 --> 38:12.160
Rewind a bit.

38:15.520 --> 38:16.640
Here.

38:21.880 --> 38:24.040
It looks like a cigarette.

38:24.120 --> 38:26.400
Can you tell which brand it is?

38:28.960 --> 38:31.480
No. No way.

38:32.960 --> 38:33.920
No way.

38:43.640 --> 38:44.600
It looks like

38:46.080 --> 38:48.000
marks left by a medical paste.

38:53.400 --> 38:54.400
What are you doing?

38:54.480 --> 38:56.120
Did I sign this before you gave it
to the Forensic Department?

38:56.200 --> 38:57.880
Is the Forensic Department
strapped for cash lately?

38:57.960 --> 38:59.960
He Yuanhang! We're not done studying it.

39:00.040 --> 39:01.080
What does studying it serve?

39:02.120 --> 39:02.960
Hey!

39:07.440 --> 39:10.000
MISSING PERSONS

39:14.840 --> 39:16.160
MISSING PERSONS

39:16.240 --> 39:19.120
FEMALE: AROUND 20-25 YEARS OLD
MALE: AROUND 55-60 YEARS OLD

39:20.920 --> 39:23.360
This is your number?

39:23.440 --> 39:24.960
Yes. Should I use yours?

39:25.640 --> 39:27.040
I don't have a pager.

39:27.120 --> 39:28.560
Why do you not want to stay
in the criminal department?

39:28.640 --> 39:29.840
You're too naive.

39:33.000 --> 39:34.280
Officer He.

39:34.360 --> 39:37.600
I believe we should first figure out
the motive behind their disappearance.

39:37.680 --> 39:39.840
Isn't it clear enough? It's a prank.

39:40.440 --> 39:41.600
Then tell me.

39:41.680 --> 39:43.600
Why did the woman take off her heels
when she entered the elevator?

39:43.680 --> 39:46.120
And why did she hold the heels
with her teeth?

39:46.200 --> 39:48.840
Why did the old man press all the buttons
in the elevator before he left?

39:48.920 --> 39:50.760
Because it's a prank. Understood?

39:50.840 --> 39:52.960
Then why did they disappear
in that locked space?

39:53.040 --> 39:54.480
-Why, why, why.
-Why did they…

39:54.560 --> 39:56.240
Do you only know how to repeat why?

39:56.320 --> 39:59.120
Our priority should be to find out
how they disappear in Yuanlongli.

39:59.200 --> 40:01.080
That's redundant.

40:01.160 --> 40:04.080
Find them, and you'll know
how they disappear.

40:04.160 --> 40:05.400
Listen to me.

40:05.480 --> 40:08.560
Find them, and they
will give you the answer.

40:10.640 --> 40:11.800
Why should I listen to you?

40:13.880 --> 40:15.040
Fine.

40:18.360 --> 40:21.640
NANSHAN TYPEWRITING

40:22.560 --> 40:23.520
Wait.

40:24.240 --> 40:25.920
You see those rickshaw riders?

40:27.000 --> 40:28.840
Should we have a wager?

40:28.920 --> 40:29.920
Go to them.

40:30.000 --> 40:32.080
If you can get their names,

40:32.160 --> 40:33.960
I'll take orders from you.

40:34.040 --> 40:35.400
If you fail to do that,

40:35.480 --> 40:37.280
you take orders from me.

40:37.360 --> 40:38.360
What do you say?

40:39.560 --> 40:40.560
No, thanks.

40:43.360 --> 40:45.560
Didn't you want to find out how they left?

40:45.640 --> 40:48.720
I remember the missing persons
came on a rickshaw.

41:01.040 --> 41:02.520
Mister, where do you want to go?

41:02.600 --> 41:03.440
Mister, where do you want to go?

41:03.520 --> 41:05.560
-Mister, where do you want to go?
-Mister, where do you want to go?

41:05.640 --> 41:07.280
Hello, everyone.

41:07.360 --> 41:08.960
I am from the criminal department
of Nanshan police station.

41:09.040 --> 41:10.560
I'd like to know…

41:11.960 --> 41:12.880
Hey!

41:14.680 --> 41:15.720
Hey…

41:18.200 --> 41:19.400
Mister!

41:21.480 --> 41:22.440
Mister!

41:31.160 --> 41:33.840
Do you understand why I didn't leave
the police station's number?

41:33.920 --> 41:36.040
You look like an imperial envoy
who visits a village.

41:36.120 --> 41:38.080
Wearing a pair of slacks
won't make it easier to catch a criminal.

41:38.160 --> 41:39.640
You look posh.

41:39.720 --> 41:41.520
You speak like an officer,

41:41.600 --> 41:43.880
and you couldn't even get the names
of those rickshaw riders.

41:43.960 --> 41:45.720
You're telling me you want
to investigate the case?

41:49.360 --> 41:52.080
Officer He, when I was studying,

41:52.160 --> 41:54.520
I looked into renowned cases of missing
persons, both local and international.

41:54.600 --> 41:56.840
Specifically, their psychology
and behavior.

41:56.920 --> 41:59.760
My judgment tells me that
the Yuanlongli case isn't just a prank.

42:00.360 --> 42:05.320
Have you looked into the missing person
case in Weinan Street, Weiyang City?

42:07.240 --> 42:08.080
No.

42:08.160 --> 42:09.600
Do you know why?

42:10.920 --> 42:13.160
After I was assigned
to Weiyang, for 22 years,

42:13.240 --> 42:17.080
whenever someone or even a pet

42:17.160 --> 42:21.720
in my district went missing,
I could find them with my eyes closed.

42:21.800 --> 42:24.720
I didn't need to study
renowned missing person cases.

42:25.360 --> 42:28.640
But hanging up posters
and waiting for calls is too passive.

42:28.720 --> 42:30.840
And your initiatives
bring trouble to others.

42:30.920 --> 42:32.160
To whom?

42:32.240 --> 42:34.080
When you sent the evidence
to the Forensic Department,

42:34.160 --> 42:35.320
why did you leave my name?

42:37.200 --> 42:40.160
I only came here yesterday.
They won't acknowledge my signature.

42:44.080 --> 42:46.400
Get out of the car.
Get yourself back to the station

42:46.480 --> 42:48.480
and withdraw all analysis requests
under my name.

42:50.720 --> 42:52.800
Take me to Yuanlongli.
I'll examine the scene again.

42:52.880 --> 42:54.760
Did I owe you a favor? Get out of the car.

42:54.840 --> 42:56.800
It's an official vehicle.
Why should I leave?

42:56.880 --> 42:58.120
Official vehicle?

42:58.200 --> 42:59.680
This is my personal car.

42:59.760 --> 43:01.320
I paid for the petrol from my own pocket.

43:01.400 --> 43:03.080
And I printed these things
with my own money.

43:03.160 --> 43:06.360
You think you're the only one
with integrity? I have it too.

43:07.760 --> 43:09.200
Get out of the car.

43:10.520 --> 43:11.640
Officer He.

43:11.720 --> 43:13.640
Based on my deduction,

43:13.720 --> 43:15.640
the unusual behavior
from those two missing persons

43:15.720 --> 43:18.200
seems to be motivated
by some external coercion.

43:18.280 --> 43:20.360
Many homicides also started
as a missing person case.

43:20.440 --> 43:21.960
What homicide?

43:22.040 --> 43:24.640
There has never been a murder on my turf.

43:24.720 --> 43:26.960
You came, and there's a murder
all of a sudden.

43:28.280 --> 43:31.040
Murphy's law. Whatever you don't
want to happen will happen.

43:31.120 --> 43:33.280
I don’t care about your law.
I don’t care about your homicide.

43:33.360 --> 43:35.320
You lost the bet just now.

43:35.400 --> 43:38.040
So you take orders from me.
I now order you to return to the station

43:38.120 --> 43:40.240
and withdraw the analysis requests
under my name.

43:40.320 --> 43:41.240
He Yuanhang!

43:42.320 --> 43:43.720
You do not have what it takes
to be a criminal police officer.

44:39.720 --> 44:44.440
PATTIA CLUB, THAI MASSAGE
